{"tid":2229692,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"首場辯論後拜登優勢擴大 NBC民調︰拜登領先特朗普14個百分點","createTime":"2020-10-04T14:34:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T15:26:38.000Z","uid":231908,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9514113640ffa3a1770f62e72b26d0b0e356ca6a","tid":2229692,"uid":231908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T14:34:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media3.s-nbcnews.com/j/newscms/2020_40/3417306/image001_5220358df9c50f602ac825e5f8c2c28c.fit-560w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia3.s-nbcnews.com%2Fj%2Fnewscms%2F2020_40%2F3417306%2Fimage001_5220358df9c50f602ac825e5f8c2c28c.fit-560w.png&h=0f99c2c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國大選形勢不利於總統特朗普。NBC及華爾街日報聯合舉辦的10月最新民意調查顯示，民主黨參選人拜登的支持度較特朗普高14個百分點，差距較上一個月時8個百分點有所擴闊。<br />\n<br />\n調查於上周三（9月30日）至周四（10月1日）舉行，對800名註冊選民進行了電話調查，誤差幅度為正負3.46個百分點。拜登獲得了全國53％的登記選民的支持，而特朗普則只有39％。該調查在周二（9月29日）的首次總統辯論之後舉行，但在特朗普宣布確診新冠肺炎之前結束。<br />\n<br />\n有大約四分之三的受訪者（73％）表示，辯論對他們的投票的意向沒有影響。另有19％受訪者稱這使他們更有可能支持拜登，而6％的人表示這使他們更有可能支持特朗普。<br />\n<br />\n同時，根據RealClearPolitics的數據，拜登在數個關鍵搖擺州的民意調查中遙遙領先，其中包括賓夕法尼亞州，密歇根州，威斯康星州和亞利桑那州。 <br />\n<br />\n由於最新民意調仍未計入特朗普確診新冠肺炎的因素，暫未知對選情會否有重大影響。<br />\n<br />\n值得注意的是，美國總統大選中的副總統辯論將於周三（10月7日）如期舉行。另外，特朗普可能會不得不在暫停競選活動一段時間，外界亦相當關注此段期間的變化。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/meet-the-press/biden-s-national-lead-over-trump-jumps-14-points-after-n1242018\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fmeet-the-press%2Fbiden-s-national-lead-over-trump-jumps-14-points-after-n1242018&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wil%2BdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=d1a2fcb9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/meet-the-press/biden-s-national-lead-over-trump-jumps-14-points-after-n1242018</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gifer.com/fxzc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gifer.com%2Ffxzc.gif&h=440f8cc0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ffd9459db390d3e6426453c9cb07671fe21a92f","tid":2229692,"uid":250865,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T14:47:28.000Z","msg":"Fake news NBC"},{"pid":"227cffdf6dea999412c8a6b422b38853232a0775","tid":2229692,"uid":250865,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T14:48:17.000Z","msg":"Fake news, dishonest media. NSDNC"},{"pid":"ae69c8f9283c47a88d5bf598ee3a7cb59bbdde61","tid":2229692,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T14:50:05.000Z","msg":"Pelosi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c8c48a1c762e20bb874e265587550c4de376835","tid":2229692,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T15:26:38.000Z","msg":"我地有冇plan b<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}